\frac{n}{n+1}=\frac{a_{n+1}-a_n}{a_{n-1}-a_n}\\a_{n-1}-a_n>a_{n+1}-a_n\\a_{n-1}>a_{n+1}
a_{n-1}\not=a_n
a_{n-1}=a_n
