a_n>a_{n+1}\\(n+1)a_{n+1}-na_{n-1}>a_{n+1}\\na_{n+1}>na_{n-1}\\a_{n+1}>a_{n-1} \implies a_n<a_{n+1}\implies a_{n-1}<a_n<a_{n+1}
